title: Ion Shine® by Conair Instant Heat Compact Styling Setter
description: When you're on the go and there's no time to stop at the stylist's, just plug in this set of 12 multi-size rollers to give your hair an instant refresh. The Conair Instant Heat Travel Hairsetter comes with 8 large rollers, 4 medium rollers, clips and a soft black carrying pouch with zipper and handle. Rollers have sure-grip starter strips and ceramic technology for even heat distribution. Pouch comes with inside pockets for clips and access slot in back for the cord. Dual voltage systems let you take this handy little pack worldwide. Imported. Pouch: 4-1/2Hx6W".
